  "texts": [
    "Overall, we recommend further exploration of how preference-based steering can be leveraged as a framework enabling resource-efficient, cold-start LLM personalization.",
    "B Sample Task Queries in Computational ExperimentsListing B.1 shows a sample of real user queries selected from the OASST2 dataset in the domain of lifestyle planning that were used throughout the computational experiments.",
